    rdfs:label "Condition: PulmonaryCO2_Diffusion_Process hasFunctionalState Hyper" ;
    rdfs:comment "Inferred from low EtCO2: the pulmonary CO2 diffusion process is in a hyperfunctional state (excessive CO2 washout — hypocapnia). Mapped to :PulmonaryCO2_Diffusion_Process as the closest available process instance; a dedicated CO2 elimination sub-process instance would be more precise." ;
    dev:aboutEntity :PulmonaryCO2_Diffusion_Process ;
    dev:onAttribute clin:hasFunctionalState ;
